  <brief_title>Comparison Study of Doxorubicin Versus Epirubicin-induced Cardiotoxicity in Patients With DLBCL</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase III Study Comparing CHOP Versus CEOP-induced Cardiotoxicity in Patients With Aggressive B-cell Lymphoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
